hopobject.body: Can I use your phone? hifas da terra catalogo 2016 Asked about the propsects of him being on the start-line in Scotland, Farah told the BBC on Tuesday: “I don’t know. It just depends how I come off that marathon. My aim is to do the London Marathon, and that is what I am fully focused on. It’s a bonus if I do it [the Commonwealth Games] but it is not on my list. I’ve got to come off the marathon healthy and then I’ll make a decision. You’ve just got to choose one race.”
